Welcome to the Town of Glen St. Mary, Florida's official website!  We are excited about using this site to communicate with our residents, businesses, and visitors.
At the Town of Glen St. Mary, we will always strive to provide up-to-date information on town services and how we are working to enhance your quality of life.  Check back often for updates on park and recreation activities, latest action of the Town Council, town news, and other areas of interest.
We now offer Town meeting minutes on our website to enable you to view the Town's monthly business. You will also find an Archive area organized by previous years for ease in locating specific meetings.  If you would like to speak at a Council meeting, you must review the guidelines on the attached speaker card and submit the form to the Town Clerk no less than 30 minutes prior to the meeting.
